original_title: The Hornet's Sting and the Hell It's Caused
overview: This is the story of Rose and Freya. Rose is a photographer who specializes in bondage, degradation, dehumanization, and murder. She lures unsuspecting men and women into her grasps and breaks them down until there is nothing left. Freya is her latest victim. A very naive small-town girl.
title: The Hornet's Sting and the Hell It's Caused
